@startuml object_confidence_to_failsafe_gate_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Object Confidence To Failsafe Gate Signal Flow\n(ADAS/AEB object confidence -> CGW fail-safe gate -> verification)

participant "ADAS / AEB\nobject-risk producers" as RiskCtx #F4F7FB
participant "CGW\neffective warning/fail-safe owner" as CGW #E8F7E8
participant "CoreState / Core\nfail-safe seams" as Core #FFF4CC
participant "TEST_SCN / evidence" as Evidence #E8F0FE

== Object Confidence Inputs ==

RiskCtx -> CGW : objectTrackValid\nobjectConfidence\nobjectEventCode\ndecelAssistDecisionReq
CGW -> CGW : evaluate routingPolicy /\nwarningPathStatus / failSafeMode
CGW -> CGW : if failSafeMode >= 1\nthen decel assist is gated
note right of CGW
Representative inputs
- object confidence / track validity
- decision decel request
- boundary / warning-path health
end note

== Effective Gate Ownership ==

CGW -> Core : CoreState::warningPathStatus
CGW -> Core : Core::failSafeMode
CGW -> Core : CoreState::selectedAlertEffectiveLevel / Type / GateReason
CGW -> CGW : publishFailSafeState()\npublishGatewayState()\npublishObjectSafetyState()
note right of CGW
Representative outputs
- failSafeMode
- warningPathStatus
- selectedAlertGateReason
- decelAssistReq after gating
end note

== Verification / Evidence ==

Core -> Evidence : failSafeMode / warningPathStatus /\ndeceled assist gate result
Evidence -> Evidence : ST_046 / ST_043 /\nReq_127~129 blocked/degraded checks
note right of Evidence
Typical verdict conditions
- failSafeMode >= 1
- decelAssistReq == 0
- blocked/degraded context observed
end note

note over RiskCtx, Evidence
Representative runtime chain
1. Object confidence and risk intent reach CGW
2. CGW owns the effective fail-safe gate decision
3. Core/CoreState expose the gated warning/decel seams
4. TEST_SCN consumes those seams as fail-safe evidence
end note

@enduml
